headline: CME Q2 Earnings, Revenues Beat Estimates on Higher Trading Volume
summary: CME posts Q2 beats on earnings and revenue as record trading volume and rising fees lift results amid market volatility.

headline: NYSE Content Advisory: Pre-market update + NIQ to debut, NYSE joins AI Summit
summary: The New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) provides a daily pre-market update directly from the NYSE Trading Floor. The NYSE is participating at the All In and Hill and Valley's "Winning the AI Race" Summit, capturing insights from key voices shaping the future of business, technology, and innovation.
